reviews.text: This is a Japanese casual restaurant serving Japenese food, sushi and sashimi dishes in Sheung Shui. It is inside the shopping centre and there are no views. Decor is clean an bright. service is quite swift. I ordered fr lunch a sashimi rice bowl with some extra sashimi and sushi. The taste was Ok. Prices are inexpensive.
